ZH: 如果你不去，不然我就要去。
EN: If you don't go, then I will go.

ZH: 不然的话，我们只能坐飞机去了。
EN: Otherwise, we will have to take a plane.

ZH: 你不快点准备，不然会迟到的。
EN: If you don't hurry up and get ready, you will be late.

ZH: 我们买了火车票，不然就要开车去了。
EN: We bought train tickets, otherwise we would have to drive.

ZH: 不然你就等在这里，我去帮你买。
EN: Otherwise, you can wait here and I will buy it for you.

ZH: 如果你不努力学习，不然考试肯定不会及格。
EN: If you don't study hard, then you will definitely fail the exam.

ZH: 不然我们可以换一种方式尝试一下。
EN: Otherwise, we can try a different approach.

ZH: 你不给我答复，不然我就当作同意了。
EN: If you don't give me an answer, then I will take it as agreement.

ZH: 不然我们明天一起去购物吧？
EN: Otherwise, let's go shopping together tomorrow.

ZH: 如果你不告诉我，不然我怎么知道？
EN: If you don't tell me, then how would I know?

ZH: 不然你们应该快点做出决定。
EN: Otherwise, you should make a decision quickly.

ZH: 你如果不肯配合，不然我们没法继续下去。
EN: If you don't cooperate, then we can't continue.

ZH: 不然我们今天就去旅游吧。
EN: Otherwise, let's go on a trip today.

ZH: 你要是不开车，不然我们走路去吧。
EN: If you don't drive, then let's walk.

ZH: 不然的话，我们只能取消计划了。
EN: Otherwise, we will have to cancel the plan.

ZH: 你不说清楚，不然我没法帮你。
EN: If you don't explain clearly, then I can't help you.

ZH: 不然你给我个理由，我为什么要相信你？
EN: Otherwise, give me a reason why I should believe you.

ZH: 如果你不接电话，不然我就去找你。
EN: If you don't answer the phone, then I will come find you.

ZH: 不然我们干脆换种方式试试看。
EN: Otherwise, let's try a different method.
